Last Broadcast Date: New Year's Day 2018
Two years ago, a Norwegian student called Maria With Hoen was cycling Bolivia's Death Road - a single track that winds through a mountain chain. As she rode round a bend, a most unexpected thing happened. Ronald Dlamini is a former mixed martial arts champion known as 'South Africa's Black Mamba.' At the height of his fighting career he didn't know that life had an unpleasant surprise in store for him. Image: A winding road Credit: BBC Show less